00:28:31.266 --> 00:28:39.177
I will put none of the diseases on you that I put on the Egyptians, for I am the Lord, your healer."

00:28:40.218 --> 00:28:48.910
Now, interesting about these verbs, if you listen, if you do, if you give these verbs, it's given in verse 26.

00:28:49.451 --> 00:28:51.474
This is the very, also in verse,

