Thank you back to Exodus chapter two.

00:28:53.536 --> 00:28:54.778
God heard their voice.

00:28:55.078 --> 00:28:55.979
He saved them.

00:28:56.039 --> 00:28:59.623
He gave his ear to hear them and he showed his statues.

00:28:59.643 --> 00:29:05.550
He's going to give them his law and simple to put two and two together here.

00:29:06.190 --> 00:29:11.957
Since God has saved us, since God has created and redeemed these pilgrims, redeemed this people.

00:29:12.017 --> 00:29:20.306
He's put them in the wilderness and for them to avoid the plagues of God to come upon them, all they have to do is hear and listen.

00:29:20.834 --> 00:29:24.017
Now, almost repeated twice here is to listen and give ear to God.

00:29:24.478 --> 00:29:33.968
Frank Christian, it is up to the uttermost importance that you put yourself under the preaching and teaching of God's word, that you give yourself to a ministry.

00:29:34.249 --> 00:29:34.949
I mean, think about it.

00:29:34.990 --> 00:29:38.734
How long did it take them to become bitter, to forsake God?

00:29:39.114 --> 00:29:40.335
Three days.

00:29:41.256 --> 00:29:42.658
Can you think about Adam and Eve in the garden?

00:29:42.678 --> 00:29:44.400
How long did it take them to sin?

00:29:44.880 --> 00:29:45.461
Think about it.

00:29:45.481 --> 00:29:45.801
One day.

00:29:46.462 --> 00:29:48.985
One day, and they weren't in there for years and months.

00:29:49.005 --> 00:29:50.066
One day and they were out.

00:29:50.370 --> 00:29:52.392
Friend, how quick we go astray.

00:29:53.173 --> 00:29:55.655
We need God's word to remind us here, don't we?

00:29:55.675 --> 00:29:56.516
We need God's word.

00:29:56.536 --> 00:29:58.598
We need to give ourselves here so that he can be.

00:29:58.618 --> 00:29:59.919
And this is really a lesson here.

00:29:59.939 --> 00:30:01.501
He says, I am Jehovah Rafa.

00:30:01.521 --> 00:30:02.322
I am your healer.

00:30:02.342 --> 00:30:04.904
This is really a lesson from the lesser to the greater.

00:30:05.625 --> 00:30:08.208
You see, this is not the first time they grumbled.

00:30:08.228 --> 00:30:09.309
This is the first time we get the word.

00:30:09.529 --> 00:30:11.531
You remember they grumbled on the other side of the Red Sea.

00:30:12.232 --> 00:30:13.693
Moses, you brought us out here to kill us.

00:30:13.793 --> 00:30:15.595
They want enough grays back there in Egypt.

00:30:15.615 --> 00:30:16.696
You brought us out here to kill us.

