This is what God had planned for them.

00:31:54.322 --> 00:31:56.325
If they would have said, God, where's the water?

00:31:56.605 --> 00:32:00.631
God said, I got the Oasis right up ahead if y'all just follow me just a little bit longer.

00:32:01.212 --> 00:32:03.014
This is what God had for them.

