Now, I think the message here is pretty clear in the symbolism of these

00:32:05.954 --> 00:32:06.895
of what they see here.

00:32:06.956 --> 00:32:12.284
There's 12 palm trees, 12 tribes, 12 springs, excuse me, 12 tribes of Israel.

