00:32:26.686 --> 00:32:27.327
God knows him.

00:32:27.447 --> 00:32:28.388
He knows the tribes.

00:32:28.428 --> 00:32:29.190
He knows the elders.

00:32:29.210 --> 00:32:31.233
He knows, this isn't everybody gets a palm tree.

00:32:31.493 --> 00:32:33.075
This is God saying, listen, I know you.

00:32:33.937 --> 00:32:34.738
I know what you need.

00:32:34.946 --> 00:32:37.971
This morning, some of you say three days of going without water.

00:32:38.311 --> 00:32:41.496
I more understand going 40 years without water, because that's how my life's been.

00:32:41.916 --> 00:32:43.158
Listen, here's what you need to hear this morning.

00:32:43.439 --> 00:32:44.480
God knows his children.

00:32:45.342 --> 00:32:46.584
God knows his people.

00:32:47.024 --> 00:32:48.266
He knows what you can endure.

00:32:48.546 --> 00:32:50.049
He knows what he's putting you through.

00:32:50.389 --> 00:32:55.677
And just like we sung earlier, Lord, how long are you gonna put your worm to death?

00:32:55.737 --> 00:32:57.139
How much more are you gonna put me through?

00:32:57.860 --> 00:33:01.105
I'm answering the prayer for increased faith and grace.

00:33:03.289 --> 00:33:04.210
Question this morning.

00:33:05.282 --> 00:33:06.063
Do you have peace?

00:33:07.885 --> 00:33:13.171
The Bible says there really truly is no peace with God unless you have faith in Christ.

00:33:14.853 --> 00:33:24.163
This morning, if you've never put your faith in Christ, everybody sitting beside you, every member of this church would love to discuss that with you, how you can have true peace with God.

00:33:24.563 --> 00:33:27.647
The question also is today is, do you have peace with others?

00:33:27.867 --> 00:33:29.969
Is there any hostility in their heart?

00:33:30.009 --> 00:33:34.354
Is there any forgiveness you need to grant this morning or forgiveness you need to ask?

00:33:37.122 --> 00:33:40.368
Lastly friends, we were made to yearn for this Oasis.

00:33:40.388 --> 00:33:45.156
We were made to yearn for this, but we know this is not the final resting place.

00:33:45.737 --> 00:33:49.223
The final resting place is with Christ and with God.

00:33:49.624 --> 00:33:52.329
Let us search our heart this morning and get rid of all bitterness.

00:33:52.369 --> 00:33:55.695
Father, thank you for the opportunity to open this word to be challenged by it.

00:33:56.116 --> 00:33:59.822
Thank you for the work that you've done in my life this week as I've studied this passage.

00:33:59.842 --> 00:34:02.066
Father, I pray your people will do well on this word

00:34:02.274 --> 00:34:04.957
and that you would search them and know them in your Holy Spirit.

00:34:04.977 --> 00:34:13.166
