00:34:13.206 --> 00:34:17.151
Father, search us and know us and lead us and guide us in your Word.

00:34:17.852 --> 00:34:30.386
Help us to experience your grace, to understand and grow in your grace and in Christ and what we have in Christ and the riches that are ours in Christ so that we may give forgiveness and grace to others.

00:34:30.626 --> 00:34:34.368
So therefore you can be glorified and your gospel can go forward.

